sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."uri" = $1 AND "statuses"."id" != $2 LIMIT $3
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "media_attachments" WHERE "media_attachments"."status_id" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT "tags"."id" FROM "tags" WHERE LOWER("tags"."name") IN (LOWER('cats'), LOWER('dogs'))

SELECT "statuses"."id", "statuses"."updated_at" FROM "statuses" INNER JOIN "accounts" ON "accounts"."id" = "statuses"."account_id" INNER JOIN "statuses_tags" ON "statuses_tags"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."visibility" = $1 AND "accounts"."suspended_at" IS NULL AND "accounts"."silenced_at" IS NULL AND "statuses_tags"."tag_id" IN ($2, $3) AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM statuses_tags forbidden WHERE forbidden.status_id = statuses.id AND forbidden.tag_id IN (NULL))) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND ("statuses"."local" = $4 OR "statuses"."uri" IS NULL) GROUP BY "statuses"."id" ORDER BY "statuses"."id" DESC LIMIT $5
